5336 and 5330 Arthur Kill Road (foreground), at, and adjoining the S.E. corner of Yetman Avenue. No. 5336, the corner house, is the H.R. Yetman home (1917 and 1907). It was earlier (1898 and 1874) the
Wm. Joline residence.
June 6, 1936
P. L. Sperr
